title: I Bet You Think About Me (Taylor's Version) (From The Vault)
description:
Taylor is over the sadness and bitterness following a breakup, and she knows that it is his loss! There are so many Easter eggs and clues and brazen statements made in this music video too.. We break it all down!
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? There are lots of ways to reach us!
